{"tid":1842540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屋企人依個時候仲返大陸。。。","createTime":"2020-01-25T17:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T07:38:57.000Z","uid":294714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d65537c25fe98a37277cd393f9eb8dc1dd58a828","tid":1842540,"uid":294714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"真心<br />\n叫左佢哋咪撚返大陸 係都唔聽<br />\n攞左幾個口罩走就覺得會無事<br />\n大佬呀 你返大陸同人食飯 點都會除低個罩啦下話<br />\n點防呀？<br />\n搞到有病嘅話又累死埋我<br />\n都係三十六計 走為上計<br />\n既然佢哋唔打算返黎之後自我隔離<br />\n咁我唯有走先啦<br />\n各位有屋住人返左大陸嘅手足 走得就好走喇<br />\n呢隻支那病毒真係唔小野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得帶口罩 勤洗手 廁所板冚好 用漂白水消毒</span><br />\n千祈唔好死係隻支那病毒手 仲要留返條命仔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2e879f3076bad1e86d58db6651007eac6cc2d10","tid":1842540,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"襯佢哋返去嗰陣換門鎖"},{"pid":"8d54474007cd84e65ab44565284fb046bb85c2fd","tid":1842540,"uid":17884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"我都有一樣煩惱<br />\n屋企人講極都唔聽 兩兄弟勸左幾日<br />\n係咪要出動到剪卡先阻止到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3c7c475846b98c8711a51605440139e28311e2","tid":1842540,"uid":319824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"仲係學生 我都想走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102fb2aa340cc1783a3e61270879f2f42a98b9b4","tid":1842540,"uid":294714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d54474007cd84e65ab44565284fb046bb85c2fd","tid":1842540,"uid":17884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:59:30.000Z","msg":"我都有一樣煩惱<br />\n屋企人講極都唔聽 兩兄弟勸左幾日<br />\n係咪要出動到剪卡先阻止到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img